{
  "stem": "3012.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when you had your language exams, you got an additional pay, which was 30% after the high degree.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That-- that's how they-- they classified it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had medium, middle, and high marks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the high marks brought you a 30% increase in your salary per language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a chance to go to the West.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always a feeling among us that we want to get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother and my aunt had a cousin who survived the camp and eventually got to Holland and got married there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to visit them, and that's the first time I had contact with the West.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in '58.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I went home, we started talking about it in great detail.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it took us a number of years to really decide what we want to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were no possibilities to leave the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Between '49 and '56, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Iron Curtain was rolled down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You couldn't even escape, unless you wanted to risk your life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then there was a possibility in '56, which we-- we couldn't-- couldn't make.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from '57 on, we started hearing rumors that if you have a close relative or you have some connection in Budapest you may, you may not be able to get a passport and immigrate.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You also had to get an exit permit from the communists.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened, again, we got the affidavits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, you couldn't get a visa, of course, from America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So through some legal maneuver and through lawyers, we got three Honduran visas sent to us on legitimate paper, with a letter of invitation from Tegucigalpa, mailed in Tegucigalpa, that relatives want us to come to them.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
